! Code Blocks

```javascript
function greet(name) {
    console.log(`Hello, ${name}!`);
    return { greeting: "hello", recipient: name };
}
```

```css
.my-class {
    color: blue;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #000);
}
```

```
Plain code block without language specification.
All formatting is preserved literally.
