! Typed Blocks

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki
This content will be parsed as //wikitext//.
With ''formatting'' and [[links]].
$$$

$$$application/javascript
// This is JavaScript code
const x = { key: "value" };
$$$

$$$text/html
<div>Raw HTML content</div>
<script>alert('Hello');</script>
$$$

